        <abstract> 
<p>If JM disapproves of inserting CD’s geological works on back of title-page [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, 3d ed.], he should strike them out. CD cares little. Reminds him to insert "additions and corrections" in advertisements. Sends list for presentation copies.</p>  
<p>Asks whether his <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> has sold at all satisfactorily.</p> 
